      "chrome": "none",
      "footer": "none",
      "html": "<section class='fn'><div class='fn__veil'></div><div class='fn__grain'></div><div class='fn__meta'><span class='fn__index'>[06]</span><span class='fn__rule'></span></div><h2 class='fn__title'>창업자는 자기 확신보다<br />시장의 준비도에 먼저<br />정직해야 한다</h2><p class='fn__body'>좋은 아이디어와 좋은 팀도 시장의 문이 닫혀 있으면 너무 일찍 죽는다. timing을 운으로 치부하는 순간, 시장을 읽는 책임도 같이 포기하게 된다. 먼저 물어야 할 것은 얼마나 멋진가가 아니라, 지금 열렸는가다.</p><div class='fn__source'><div class='fn__source-label'>SOURCE</div><div class='fn__source-body'>Bill Gross, TED<br />The single biggest reason why start-ups succeed</div></div></section>",
      "css": ".fn{position:relative;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#151210 0%,#0f0c0b 100%);color:#f2eee7;padding:90px 78px 96px;font-family:'Pretendard','Malgun Gothic',sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden}.fn__veil{position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 78% 18%,rgba(255,218,187,.08),rgba(255,218,187,0) 18%),radial-gradient(circle at 18% 72%,rgba(255,255,255,.04),rgba(255,255,255,0) 24%)}.fn__grain{position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.14) .65px,transparent .95px),radial-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.18) .9px,transparent 1.15px),repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.018) 0 1px,transparent 1px 3px);background-size:2px 2px,4px 4px,3px 100%;mix-blend-mode:soft-light;opacity:.78;pointer-events:none}.fn__meta,.fn__title,.fn__body,.fn__source{position:relative}.fn__meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px}.fn__index{font-size:28px;line-height:1;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.035em}.fn__rule{height:2px;flex:1;background:rgba(242,238,231,.82)}.fn__title{margin:40px 0 0;max-width:860px;font-size:72px;line-height:1.04;letter-spacing:-.062em;font-weight:800;word-break:keep-all}.fn__body{margin:28px 0 0;max-width:860px;font-size:29px;line-height:1.7;letter-spacing:-.02em;color:rgba(242,238,231,.8);font-weight:500;word-break:keep-all}.fn__source{margin-top:42px;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid rgba(242,238,231,.18);max-width:620px}.fn__source-label{font-family:'neue-haas-grotesk-display','Helvetica Neue','Arial',sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.1;font-weight:300;letter-spacing:.22em;color:rgba(242,238,231,.52)}.fn__source-body{margin-top:12px;font-size:20px;line-height:1.7;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:rgba(242,238,231,.92);font-weight:500}"
